  "description": [
    "Christmas Edition Of To be Issued Sunday December 17th Will be the most comprehensive newspaper ever issued in Alabama if not in the whole South Beautiful colored comic supplement the most intensely interesting array of Christmas reading all prepared expressly for this issue of The Advertiser beautiful and timely illustrations and the entire edition printed on fine paper bought for the occasion Circulation 25000 Guaranteed Figuring on the usually accepted basis of five readers to each paper sent out this issue of The Advertiser will be read by more than 125000 persons Think of presenting your business announcement to such a large number of representative people The best and cheapest advertising proposition ever offered to the business men of the South Every General Business Should be Represented Dont put it off Attend to it today Early copy ensures the best positions and the most attractive typographical effect The Advertising Department the Art Department the Ad Writing Department and the Engraving Department are all at your service Write wire or telephone 867 Solicitors sent anywhere THE FIGURES OF NORTH CENSUS BULLETIN ON COTTON OINNED TO DECEMBER 1 MS4342 Contlw Round Bairs as Half BalmA Statement Is Issurd by The Agricultural Depart"
